@node Synthetic_Art "Synthetic Art."

                        @{i}--- SYNTHETIC ART. ---@{ui}


  Synthetic Art. is a french association, mainly composed of programmers,
dedicated to the Amiga.

  Our only goal is to have fun in programming this fabulous machine and try
to offer you quality software.

  Right now, our public production is composed of:

  * this piece of sofware.

  * @{b}PDBase@{ub}, a program to catalogue, store and retrieve files on archive
