@node Greetings

    First I've to thanks Christian Buchner for his fabulous @{"ADPCM" link "ADPCM" 0} package.

    Thanks to the GNU team for his marvelous C++ compiler.
    All these programs were made with gcc compiler using optimisation
level 3.

    Thanks to jerome of Synthetic Art. for his support and for having
supported my questions.

    Note that I only had tried this piece of software on my A4000/40, and
I don't know if an A500 would run fast enough, but an A1200 should run it
really easy.
    If you get any trouble, contact me.

@endnode


